public class Abc
{

   public static void main(String[] args)
   {
   
      Entry&lt;String, Integer&gt; e = null;
      //Map.Entry&lt;String, Integer&gt; e = null;
   
   }

}
```


  [1]: https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/technotes/guides/language/static-import.html

